STATE
v.
Bobby Birdeille KELLY. No. 529P00-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2009. Catherine F. Jordan, Assistant Attorney General, Sam Currin, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 16th day of September 2008 by Defendant for "Petition and/or Request for Rehearing":
